law.text: The county clerk shall forward a copy of each approved application to the Department of Revenue and to the office of the Attorney General within ten (10) days of approval.
law.history: Amended 2005 Ky. Acts ch. 85, sec. 692, effective June 20, 2005. -- Created 1986 Ky. Acts ch. 70, sec. 5, effective July 15, 1986.
